    "By the Apache 2.0 license, any modified derivatives must indicate their modifications prominently and preserve all original copyright notices.",
    "The conversation tree is the fundamental data structure in Open Assistant.The researchers [7] evaluated the zero-shot performance of ChatGPT and Open Assistant within the domain of Computational Social Science classification tasks.",
    "Additionally, they examined the effects of different prompting strategies.",
    "Their experiment encompassed several factors, such as prompt complexity.",
    "This involved investigating the outcomes of incorporating label definitions into the prompt, utilizing synonyms for label names, and exploring the influence of integrating memories during the training of the foundation model."
